item.title: E04292
item.description: John Deere 1630 High Crop Tractor, canopy, powersteering, 3 cylinder JD engine, 3 point linkage, PTO, toplink, hydr.spoolvalves, 7.50-16 front tyres and 11.2R44 (270/95R44) rear tyres 80% remaining. Tractor is in very good technical and clean condition. Very clean original tractor!

item.title: E04513
item.description: Fordson E27, 2WD, petrol engine, mechanically refurbished tractor, 3-point linkage, PTO, brand new tyres, rear tyres 13.6-36, front tyres 6.00-19. Electric system needs attention. Inspections are welcome.

item.title: V00060
item.description: Lanz Bulldog D9506, 45PS halbraupe, gutes laufwerk, baujahr 1951, 6 gang getriebe, guter original zustand, schone patina, lauft gut, kuhler sind schon, 7.50-20 forder rader. Schlepper kann jeder zeit besichtigt werden.
